<title type="html"><![CDATA[Re: Canvas removal]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/viewtopic.php?t=4977&amp;p=7852#p7852"><![CDATA[
If you want to clear the canvas, use clearRect <dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>context.clearRect(0, 0, canvas.width, canvas.height);</code></dd></dl><br />or set width or height on the canvas <dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>canvas.width = canvas.width;</code></dd></dl><br /><br />If you want to remove a canvas, remove it from the document and drop all references to it.<br /><dl class="codebox"><dt>Code: </dt><dd><code>canvas.parentNode.removeChild(canvas);<br />canvas = context = null;</code></dd></dl><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forums.whatwg.org/bb3/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=4">zcorpan</a> — Mon Mar 19, 2012 7:24 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
